<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">https://www.macquariedictionary.com.au/resources/view/word/of/the/year/</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">https://www.theguardian.com/australia-news/2020/nov/17/iso-named-2020s-word-of-the-year-by-australian-national-dictionary-centre</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">https://www.theguardian.com/books/2020/nov/23/oed-says-2020-too-many-potential-words-of-the-year-to-name-just-one-oxford-english-dictionary</span></p>
